# Automation Scripts

## Overview

This repository contains automation and operational scripts used throughout the Kubernetes HomeLab.

Scripts are used to automate:

- Cluster deployment
- Node configuration
- Monitoring setup
- Backup operations
- Security checks
- Networking tasks
- Maintenance workflows

